eZ GPG extension v0.4.5 FEATURES
=================================================

Security
* GPG/PGP Compatible Encryption
* Secure - Does not write unencrypted data to disk
* Secure - Avoids unessisary unencrypted memory usage
* Secure - Does not write encrypted data to disk

Functionality
* Encryption and Decryption Methods
* Encryption and Decryption Template Operators


Support
=================================================

There are many additional features we would
like to add to eZ GPG.

A few users of eZ GPG may require further
development of the eZ GPG extension.

If you are interested in sponsoring the development
of any of these features for your eZ publish web site,
please contact info@brookinsconsulting.com
